            | We may collect additional personal information to process any of your orders, subscriptions and payments. We may use and share information as necessary to fulfill your orders and complete your payments. We may also collect additional information from you when you ask for support, share feedback, enter contests, participate in forums, complete surveys, or subscribe to newsletters and mailing lists.
            | We will automatically record your Site usage and collect your IP address, browser type and operating system, dates and times, and referring and exit pages/links and URLs. We use this information to maintain and improve the Sites and will not share personal information together with this information.
