            | We use the other information we collect to operate our Site, including to provide our games and services, respond to your requests, process orders and payments, update you about new games and other news, process your input and feedback, and to personalize our services. We will use your information as may otherwise be described in this Privacy Policy from time to time or as explicitly described at the time that we collect information from you. We use both your personal information and other non-personal information that we collect to improve the quality and design of the Site and to create new features, promotions, and services by storing, tracking, and analyzing user preferences and trends.
            | We may also combine or associate the information you submit to us through the Site with other information we have collected from you in through other forums, such as emails or offline, or with publicly available information or other information we may obtain from third parties.
        .privacy-subtitle Email And Mailing List Policies
        .content We will communicate with you via email for any purpose relating to your account and for customer service. You may also be emailed about updates, new games, features and other services we are offering from time to time. If you choose to subscribe to any newsletter or other mailing list, your email will be used exclusively for the purpose of sending you the messages that you request. Your email will not be sold to any third-party.
            | Except for certain required emails about your account, the Site and related services, you may unsubscribe from any of our other mailing or distribution lists at any time. If you want to opt-out of receiving email messages from us, please follow the particular opt-out instructions set forth in the message itself or email us at privacy@arq.su from the email address that you would like to remove and let us know you want to “unsubscribe” or “opt-out”. If you wish to update or delete an email address for any reason, please email privacy@arq.su.
        .privacy-subtitle Sharing
