            | We will share personal information with trusted agents and other service providers that are providing services to us or acting on our behalf. These service providers will be prohibited from using any personal information for purposes unrelated to the service they are providing.
            | We may share some or all of your personal information with any parent company, subsidiaries, joint ventures, or other similar related entity or affiliate company under common control provided that each such entity with access to your personal information agrees to follow this Privacy Policy. If we go through a change of control/ownership transition, such as a merger, acquisition, reorganization, sale of all or a portion of our assets or similar transaction, your personal information will likely be shared with the resulting entity provided that it agrees to follow this Privacy Policy.
            | If we are required by law to disclose your personal information, we will try to let you know by of email first (unless prohibited from doing so) to give you a chance to object. If you do not challenge the request, we may be required to disclose your information. We may share your information if we believe in good faith that such disclosure is necessary to protect our rights or interests, to report suspected illegal or wrongful activity, or to report any instance in which the rights, interests or property of a third party may be in danger.
            | Unless you tell us to at the time we collect information from you or as necessary part of a particular service or feature you choose to use or be included in on the Site, we will not share your personal information with others for their own commercial or marketing purposes. We may provide information to other third parties to provide the services that you have specifically requested or to whom you explicitly ask us to send your information.
        .privacy-subtitle International Users
        .content Anyone using the Site from outside of the Russian Federation should be aware that personal information may be stored and processed in the Russian Federation or any other country in which we or our agents maintain facilities, and by using the Site, you consent to any such transfer of information outside of your country.
